Package: rdrugshortages
Type: Package
Title: Access Drug Shortage Report Databases
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Jon", "Pipitone", email = "jon@pipitone.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jon Pipitone <jon@pipitone.ca>
Description: Provides programmatic access to drug shortage report databases via web API. Results are returned as flat data tables to make analysis easy. The package currently supports the following countries: Canada.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
